social_posts.post_text:
Being on spring break means you have to do the things that bring you joy…even if that means carried a 20 lbs vest up a mountain 😅 When Katie and I first met we went on a hike. Yes, as cliché as that sounds our first date was a hike. We both thought that the hike was maybe going to last 2 hours…it lasted 9 and ended with solid Mexican food. This was almost three years and on the same mountain. Now we’re married and looking forward to what life brings us.

#mr.mctiktok #hiking #marriedcouple #hikingcouple #sandiego #sandiegolife #cowelsmountain #teacherspringbreak #katieandkev

Our last night on the Disney cruise we ate at the one and only Tiana’s place and met Tiana herself! 

@disneyparks @disneycruiseline #disney100 #hosted #tianasplace #cruise #mardigras

Happy Easter everyone!! We love you! We’re stoked to share a moment from our first married Easter with you! We hope your day is spent with joy and little silliness sprinkled in. 

#mrmctiktok #happyeaster #firstmarriedeaster2023 #katieandkev #marriedcouple #sundayfunday #socal #california

Spring break is for hiking and exploring. Another great day hiking with my beautiful wife! 😊 

Man, do I love being a teacher! Not only do I get the privilege of mentoring and teaching young minds, I also get built in breaks from work!

#mrmctiktok #hiking #lagunabeach #teacherspringbreak #saturdayisforthewife #california #southerncalifornia #orangecounty

Rounding off our spring break hiking adventures back in beautiful sunny San Diego!

We were so so blessed to enjoy 75 degree weather on this hike! 😱 Now I get to enjoy a sweet sunburn 😒 but it was so worth it!

Katie and I hiked all around mission trails (including South Furtuna Peak) which was the site of our first date 🥰

I couldn’t ask to live in a more beautiful place or have a more beautiful life! 😋

#missiontrails #hiking #sandiego #marriedcouple #springbreak #teacherspringbreak
